  },
  {
    q: "How do I find a commission-only coffee sales agency?",
    a: "Commission-only specialty coffee sales agencies are rare relative to the number of roasters who could benefit from them. The best way to find one is through your network — roaster associations, SCA events, and regional barista competitions all surface people embedded in the industry's sales side. Look for agencies with documented track records of account placement in your target markets, and ask for references from roasters they've represented."
  },
